            <mrow>u_1:  =\amp (1,0,0)</mrow>
            <mrow>u_2: =\amp  e_2-\frac{\inner{u_2\cdot e_2}{u_1}}{\norm{u_1}^2}u_1=(0,1,0)-\frac{-1}{2}(1,0,0)=(1/2,1,0)</mrow>
